Microsoft Office 2000 Personal was an additional SKU, solely designed for the Japanese market, that included Word 2000, Excel 2000 and Outlook 2000.<ref>{{cite web|title=Office 2000 - Microsoft Office 2000 Personal|url=http://www.microsoft.com/japan/Office/previous/2000/Personal/package.mspx|work=Microsoft Japan|publisher=Microsoft Japan|accessdate=June 14, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070218061809/http://www.microsoft.com/japan/Office/previous/2000/Personal/package.mspx|archivedate=February 18, 2007|location=Internet Archive|language=Japanese}}</ref> This compilation would later become widespread as Microsoft Office 2003 Basic.

